Folder structure to be used

-> bench (for Modelsim test benches)
-> doc (for design documentation)
-> hardware (for PCB/Schematic Data)
   |
   -> doc (hardware specific documentation)
   -> manufacturing_data (Gerbers/BoMs to actaully get the boards made)
   -> rawcard (the pcb data, format/tool to be decided)
   -> schem (the schematic data, format/tool to be decided)
-> rtl (for source files)
-> syn (synthesised code and project settigns)
   |
   -> <target> (specific to target device; may be multiple of these)